Extraction of $\mathrm{Zn}$ from zinc blends is achieved by roasting followed by reduction with carbon. Reactions involved are :
$$
\begin{aligned}
& 2 \mathrm{ZnS}+3 \mathrm{O}_2 \stackrel{\text { heat }}{\longrightarrow} 2 \mathrm{ZnO}+2 \mathrm{SO}_2 \text { (Roasting) } \\
& \mathrm{ZnO}+\mathrm{C}(\text { Coke }) \stackrel{\text { heat }}{\longrightarrow} \mathrm{Zn}+\mathrm{CO} \text { (Re duction) }
\end{aligned}
$$
